 <PERSON> Tom </PERSON> <PERSON> Raum </PERSON>, a Washington-based reporter for <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION>, is covering <PERSON> George </PERSON> <PERSON> Bush </PERSON>'s presidential campaign.
