<HEAD>Two Afghan Warplanes Hit by Pakistani F-16s</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By MOHAMMED AFTAB</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>ISLAMABAD, Pakistan (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
