 group. While its ads wo n't change dramatically, <ORGANIZATION> Honda </ORGANIZATION> promotions will appear in publications such as `` 50 Plus'' magazine and on television shows such as `` Murder, She Wrote.'' <ORGANIZATION> Honda </ORGANIZATION> television ads will continue to feature the voice of actor <PERSON> Daniel </PERSON> <PERSON> J. </PERSON> <PERSON> Travanti </PERSON>, and the sights and sounds of actor <PERSON> James </PERSON> <PERSON> Garner </PERSON> still will be used in <ORGANIZATION> Mazda </ORGANIZATION> ads.
